# Rust + native binding build outputs (OPE-15/16/17). Crates and the
# napi-rs binding compile to platform-specific artifacts under target/
# and `.node` files in the binding package. None of those are checked in;
# the JS loader rebuilds the binding on demand via
# `pnpm --filter @openalice/node-bindings-analysis-core build:napi`.
target/
**/*.node
